Lao Ding lakukan.

552
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:30,800
Apa dia sedang luang?

553
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,360
Lao Ding.

554
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:37,000
Kawan kita, Liang Chen,
menemui kesulitan besar.

555
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:40,680
