Halo, Kak Jiayun.

558
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:53,680
Halo, Liang Chen.

559
00:38:54,520 --> 00:38:56,840
Kau butuh bantuanku
untuk siaran langsungmu?

560
00:38:58,680 --> 00:38:59,800
Kebetulan sekali, Lu Jing.

561
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:00,560
Kau sudah makan?

562
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:01,480
Belum.

563
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:04,320
Kau menolak tawaran
siaran idolamu?

564
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:07,600
Aku akan menunggu sampai
dia tak menemukan orang lain.

565
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,800
Anak muda yang polos.

566
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:15,280
Menurutmu, Liang Chen
takkan menemukan orang?

567
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,240
Dia mencarimu?

568
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,840
Tidak.

569
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:21,040
Orang yang mampu,
yang bisa mendapatkannya.

570
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:26,200
Ding Jiayun?

571
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:30,560
Meski pemikiranmu polos,
tapi tebakanmu tepat juga.

572
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:41,880
Kak Jiayun.

573
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,880
Ini hanya siaran biasa saja.

574
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,320
Aku tak mau merepotkanmu.

575
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:47,320
Tak apa, kebetulan aku luang.

576
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:50,440
Ini hanya hal kecil saja,
tak perlu merepotkanmu.

577
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:51,560
Chen Chen.

578
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:53,120
Tunggu sebentar, Kak Jiayun.

579
00:39:53,640 --> 00:39:54,200
Ada apa?

580
00:39:54,400 --> 00:39:55,360
Herman menelepon.

581
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:57,160
Dia bilang dia setuju
ikut kau siaran.

582
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,400
Dia setuju?

583
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,480
Benarkah?

584
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,320
Baik, tunggu.

585
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:03,520
Halo, Kak Jiayun.

586
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:04,120
Halo?

587
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:06,680
Kak Qing sudah mengaturnya untukku.

588
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,040
Namun, aku tetap
berterima kasih.

589
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,120
Tak apa.

590
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,520
Begini saja.

591
00:40:15,040 --> 00:40:15,800
Sampai jumpa.

592
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,220
Mengapa dia akhirnya setuju?

593
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:48,240
♪Aku berdiri di atas panggung♪

594
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:52,000
♪Bernyanyi dengan pelan♪

595
